message.body: HAPPY GRADUATION! And happy almost birthday!!! xoxo <3 Sarah
I will text you next week then :D are you done with work? Do you have some sort of senior week?

Yup. Tonights's the start of our senior week, I'm really excited. As we speak I am hanging up my artwork from an independent study in design to do a final crit and show it to family and friends. That's the last thing I've got to do. :)
